data.description: *Back on the market due to buyers financing falling through.* Adorable home with huge 30 x 60 pole barn! Located at Loon Lake this home sits on a .649 acre lot directly across the street from the water. Home was built in 2005 and offers 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and a full basement that has drywall and flooring, just needs a few finishing touches! Some features/updates to the home include: new metal roof in 2021, new asphalt driveway in 2021, new waterproof vinyl flooring in kitchen & living room, and Generac generator. If you need storage/shop space, you will love the oversized 2 car attached garage as well as the 30x60 pole building with electricity, separate workroom, and 2 separate overhead doors. This property has much to offer, be sure to check it out!
